Dialogue: 11,0:22:52.51,0:22:56.47,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}叫び声を 拾い上げて
Dialogue: 12,0:22:56.18,0:23:01.10,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}接吻交わそう
